# Multimedia Assets

- Product images in `public/products/{sku}/`; use WebP with PNG fallback via `<picture>`.
- Alt text bilingual via i18n: describe bat model, color, and league (LMB Sultanes jersey).
- Max hero ~200KB; thumbnails ~40KB; lazy-load below fold with `loading="lazy"`.

```tsx
<Image
  src={`/products/${sku}/main.webp`}
  alt={t('product.imageAlt', { name: product.name })}
  width={800}
  height={800}
  sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 50vw"
/>
```

- No EXIF GPS or staff metadata in uploads; strip on server if user-generated.
- Video: short loops for glove web patterns; host on Netlify CDN or signed URL, not hotlinked.
